    <title>hexo的Next主题美化</title>
    <link href="http://emary.xyz/2020/08/06/hexo%E7%9A%84Next%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/"/>
    <id>http://emary.xyz/2020/08/06/hexo%E7%9A%84Next%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/</id>
    <published>2020-08-06T08:35:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-08-09T08:35:33.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录在主题美化过程中的用到的设置，全文基于Next主题编写，参考了大量网络上的博文。next主题下载地址：<a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/releases">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/releases</a>  我是因为用命令一直下载失败所以直接下载解压到themes里的。</p><a id="more"></a><h4 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h4><hr><p>搭建博客的时候用了hexo人气较高的<code>next</code>主题，美化过程中遇到了各种各样的问题，在此记录并且可能会持续更新~</p><h4 id="选择Next的主题样式"><a href="#选择Next的主题样式" class="headerlink" title="选择Next的主题样式"></a>选择Next的主题样式</h4><hr><p>在 <code>\hexo\themes\next\_config.yml</code> 主题配置文件中查找关键字<code>Schemes</code>，选择自己喜欢的样式。<br>需要的样式去掉前面的#即可。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Schemes</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Muse   #默认的版本</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Mist</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Pisces</span><br><span class="line">scheme: Gemini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="代码高亮"><a href="#代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="代码高亮"></a>代码高亮</h4><hr><p>编辑站点配置文件搜索highlight：</p><p>将auto_detece启用</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">enable: true</span><br><span class="line">line_number: true</span><br><span class="line">auto_detect: true</span><br><span class="line">tab_replace: &#39;&#39;&#96;&#96;&#96;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑主题配置文件，搜索highlight_theme</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">codeblock:</span><br><span class="line"> # Code Highlight theme</span><br><span class="line">  # Available values: normal | night | night eighties | night blue | night bright | solarized | solarized dark | galactic</span><br><span class="line">  # See: https://github.com/chriskempson/tomorrow-theme</span><br><span class="line">  highlight_theme: night</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Next使用tomorrow-theme作为代码高亮，目前有normal | night | night eighties | night blue | night bright | solarized | solarized dark | galactic 种样式可供选择，我这里用的是night。</p><h4 id="添加背景图片"><a href="#添加背景图片" class="headerlink" title="添加背景图片"></a>添加背景图片</h4><hr><blockquote><p>1.将要添加的背景图片放入<code>thems/next/sources/images</code><br>2.打开<code>themes/next/sources/css/_schemes/</code>文件夹，进入你的主题，修改<code>index.styl</code></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@import &#x27;../Pisces/_layout&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">@import &#x27;../Pisces/_header&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">@import &#x27;../Pisces/_menu&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">@import &#x27;../Pisces/_sub-menu&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line">@import &#x27;../Pisces/_sidebar&#x27;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">body &#123;</span><br><span class="line"> background:url(/images/01.jpg);</span><br><span class="line">  background-attachment: fixed;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文章结束语"><a href="#文章结束语" class="headerlink" title="文章结束语"></a>文章结束语</h4><hr><blockquote><p>添加模板文件  </p></blockquote><p>在主题目录下\layout_macro中新建passage-end-tag.swig文件，并且添加以下内容：<br><img src="http://qekniae2o.bkt.clouddn.com/img/20200809110224.png" alt=""></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% if not is_index %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text-align:center;color: #ccc;font-size:14px;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>-------------　　　　本文结束　<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;fa fa-heart&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span>　步履不止　　　　-------------<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><blockquote><p>导入模板文件  </p></blockquote><p>打开<code>\next\layout\_macro\post.swig</code><br>在如下位置</p><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;#####################&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;### END POST BODY ###&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;#####################&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>的后面，<code>&lt;footer class=&quot;post-footer&quot;&gt;</code><br>的前面插入下面的代码</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#123;% if not is_index %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% include &#x27;passage-end-tag.swig&#x27; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="参考博文，博文推荐"><a href="#参考博文，博文推荐" class="headerlink" title="参考博文，博文推荐"></a>参考博文，博文推荐</h4><hr><p><a href="http://www.chenlianhan.com/2020/03/20/HEXO-NEXT%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%88%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%89/">HEXO+NEXT界面美化</a></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;记录在主题美化过程中的用到的设置，全文基于Next主题编写，参考了大量网络上的博文。next主题下载地址：&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/releases&quot;&gt;https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next/releases&lt;/a&gt;  我是因为用命令一直下载失败所以直接下载解压到themes里的。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
    
